text: 21 at 33 is the fourteenth studio album by Elton John and was released on 13 May 1980. It went to number 3 in New Zealand, number 6 in Norway, number 7 in Australia, number 10 in Canada, number 12 in the United Kingdom and number 13 in the United States. == Track listing == === Side one === === Side two === Category:1980 albums Category:Elton John albums
